                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2003-10-22</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Simply a great biography of a very great man. <p>It is a compact book of under 200 pages; squeezing Sir Winston Churchill's long and eventful life into this short book must have been hard but Keegan succeeded brilliantly.</span>
                  
              
